    <p>My Lunch In is a lunch delivery and pick-up service brought to you by Nora's Table restaurant in Hood River.</p>

    <p>You can order and pay for your lunch with a credit card here at the Web site (or by selecting "cash" and paying on delivery or pickup). Or, you can come to the restaurant and order and sit down for table service.  We are preparing and serving lunch Monday through Friday, from 11:30 to 2:00.</p>

    <p>To get lunch, order here at the web site. Choose your lunch from our oh-so-munchable menu, pick your delivery time/location, or the time you’d like to pick it up at Nora’s Table, and then pay. You’re done. Go back to work or play. If you’re picking your lunch up at Nora’s Table, it will be waiting for you when you walk in the door.</p>

    <p>Nora’s Table is located at 110 Fifth St., downtown Hood River. We are open for dinner service at 5:00, seven nights a week. Reserve a table at <a href="http://www.opentable.com/noras-table">Open Table.</a></p>
